snippet.title: Specters of the Sun Graveyard Demo Trailer 2023-06-24
snippet.description:
Specters of the Sun is a challenging 2D action platformer with action-packed levels. Take on the role of an elusive specter to reclaim your old corpse, now possessed at the heights of your former kingdom. 

Try the demo and wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2508730/Specters_of_the_Sun/

Web version: https://etclundberg.itch.io/specters-of-the-sun

Updates: https://twitter.com/HristoeL
